--e7896d2748272a89c5f5c5e16c6825a51?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobs, Career, Employment | Jobrapido.com', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobrapido.com/jobpreview/1377330687522111488?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Recruit.net', 'apply_link': 'https://www.recruit.net/job/software-engineer-salesforce--jobs/B1C214905FD5A828?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://www.roberthalf.com/sg/en/job/singapore/software-engineer-salesforce/67020-0013362657-sgen', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Robert Half'}], 'job_description': \"The CompanyOur client is a leading investment management firm with a strong regional presence. The organization places high importance on technology as a business enabler and continues to invest in its Salesforce platform to support sales, client coverage, and operational efficiency. This is a permanent, in-house position responsible for the application support, administration, and ongoing development of Salesforce Sales Cloud. The role plays a critical part in ensuring Salesforce remains stable, scalable, and aligned with the firm's asset management business requirements.The Role Provide end-to-end support, administration, and development of Salesforce Sales CloudDesign, build, and maintain Salesforce functionalities to support business processesPartner with business users to gather requirements and deliver sustainable technical solutionsManage and support integrations between Salesforce and enterprise systemsTroubleshoot production issues and drive root-cause analysis and permanent fixesContribute to platform enhancements, automation, and data optimization initiativesEnsure Salesforce solutions align with internal governance and best practiceSupport long-term platform roadmap and continuous improvement initiatives Your Profile At least 5 years of hands-on Salesforce development experience, with strong focus on Sales CloudExperience working in an asset management or investment management environmentProven experience supporting Salesforce in a permanent, enterprise settingSalesforce Platform Developer Certification (required)Strong analytical, problem-solving, and stakeholder management skillsSalesforce Sales CloudSnowflakeWorkato (iPaaS / integrations)Development C#, Front-end JavaScript jQuery Apply TodayPlease send your resume, in WORD format only and quote reference number DC13362657, by clicking the apply button. Please note that only short-listed candidates will be contacted.Robert Half International Pte Ltd. Co. Registration no.: 200612189E | EA Licence no.: 07C5595 | Dmitriy Chervinskyi EA Registration no.: R22108655By clicking 'apply', you give your express consent that Robert Half may use your personal information to process your job application and to contact you from time to time for future employment opportunities. For further information on how Robert Half processes your personal information and how to access and correct your information, please read the Robert Half privacy notice: https://www.roberthalf.com.sg/privacy-statement. Please do not submit any sensitive personal data to us in your resume (such as government ID numbers, ethnicity, gender, religion, marital status or trade union membership) as we do not collect your sensitive personal data at this time.\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3D7dv5KFL-IKxzLkSgAAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': 'MONTH', 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113200', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': 'yhz8ESsGl_xBMPIcAAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Firmware Engineering Lead', 'employer_name': 'Advanced Micro Devices, Inc', 'employer_logo': None, 'employer_website': None, 'job_publisher': 'AMD Careers', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://careers.amd.com/careers-home/jobs/76672?lang=en-us&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': True, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'AMD Careers', 'apply_link': 'https://careers.amd.com/careers-home/jobs/76672?lang=en-us&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': True}, {'publisher': 'Jobstreet', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobstreet.com/job/89318859?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/firmware-engineering-lead-singapore-advanced-micro-devices-inc-7ade91ae4bbc/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'EchoJobs', 'apply_link': 'https://echojobs.io/job/amd-firmware-engineer-s8x3u?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': True}, {'publisher': 'ClickaJobs', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.clickajobs.com/jobs/firmware-engineering-lead?id=31973553&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://careers.amd.com/careers-home/jobs/76672?lang=en-us', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'AMD Careers'}], 'job_description': 'WHAT YOU DO AT AMD CHANGES EVERYTHING\\n\\nAt AMD, our mission is to build great products that accelerate next-generation computing experiences—from AI and data centers, to PCs, gaming and embedded systems. Grounded in a culture of innovation and collaboration, we believe real progress comes from bold ideas, human ingenuity and a shared passion to create something extraordinary. When you join AMD, you’ll discover the real differentiator is our culture. We push the limits of innovation to solve the world’s most important challenges—striving for execution excellence, while being direct, humble, collaborative, and inclusive of diverse perspectives. Join us as we shape the future of AI and beyond. Together, we advance your career.\\n\\nTHE ROLE:\\n\\nWe are looking for an SMTS (Senior Member of Technical Staff) Engineer with an obsession for firmware. As part of the role, the SMTS Engineer will work closely with other firmware engineers, developers and architects across various IPs in leading the designs and implementing firmware that spans pre-silicon and post-silicon for all AMD SoCs.\\u202f\\n\\nTHE PERSON:\\n\\nYou are passionate about firmware development with creative and effective problem-solving skills, a motivated, self-starter who can work both independently and collaboratively in fast paced environments. You have excellent technical communication, interpersonal and leadership skills.\\n\\nKEY RESPONSIBILITIES:\\n• Lead Engineer responsible for designing, developing, debugging, verifying and/or validating firmware, software and/or hardware\\n• Lead day-to-day firmware development work\\n• Provide consultation to internal and external customers regarding AMD features and programming requirements\\n\\nPREFERRED EXPERIENCE:\\n• Multiple prior years of related firmware experience combined with technical education within the semiconductor industry\\n• Expert level experience producing quality firmware\\n\\nACADEMIC CREDENTIALS:\\n• Bachelor’s or Master’s degree (preferred) in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Electrical Engineering, or equivalent\\n\\nLOCATION:\\n\\nSingapore\\n\\n#LI-CK1\\n\\nBenefits offered are described: AMD benefits at a glance.\\n\\nAMD does not accept unsolicited resumes from headhunters, recruitment agencies, or fee-based recruitment services. AMD and its subsidiaries are equal opportunity, inclusive employers and will consider all applicants without regard to age, ancestry, color, marital status, medical condition, mental or physical disability, national origin, race, religion, political and/or third-party affiliation, sex, pregnancy, sexual orientation, gender identity, military or veteran status, or any other characteristic protected by law. We encourage applications from all qualified candidates and will accommodate applicants’ needs under the respective laws throughout all stages of the recruitment and selection process.\\n\\nAMD may use Artificial Intelligence to help screen, assess or select applicants for this position. AMD’s “Responsible AI Policy” is available here.\\n\\nThis posting is for an existing vacancy.', 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3Dyhz8ESsGl_xBMPIcAAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113300', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': '0XpPcxNn12sGdgJGAAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Software Engineer, Behaviors Research', 'employer_name': 'MOTIONAL SINGAPORE PTE. LIMITED', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS1FhfMzXixa21Yth6ppJOuzCrZ0tBFpJ0LqkN9&s=0', 'employer_website': None, 'job_publisher': 'MyCareersFuture', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/information-technology/software-engineer-behaviors-research-motional-singapore-5dd63ea16eb3a34386749c4912b8c254?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'MyCareersFuture', 'apply_link': 'https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/information-technology/software-engineer-behaviors-research-motional-singapore-5dd63ea16eb3a34386749c4912b8c254?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jooble', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jooble.org/jdp/-3887395488864619935?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobrapido.com', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobrapido.com/jobpreview/237963979442356224?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/information-technology/software-engineer-behaviors-research-motional-singapore-5dd63ea16eb3a34386749c4912b8c254', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'MyCareersFuture'}], 'job_description': 'What you’ll be doing:\\n• Conduct research on driving behavior related topics, such as future prediction, motion planning, agent simulation, scenario generation\\n• Work with large-scale internal datasets to demonstrate the effectiveness of your research\\n• Collaborate with different teams to deploy your research results into the autonomous vehicles\\n• Publish the research results in papers and patents\\n\\nWhat we are looking for:\\n• Enrolled in a Masters or PhD program in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Robotics or similar technical field of study\\n• Strong Machine Learning research background with publications in any of the top-tier conferences(RSS, ICRA, CoRL, CVPR, ICRL, ICML, NeurIPS, etc.)\\n• Proficiency in Python coding and PyTorch or other commonly-used deep learning frameworks\\n• One-team mindset and effective collaboration with other researchers and engineers\\n• Strong communication and interpersonal skills\\n• Previous experience in autonomous driving is preferred', 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': '27 days ago', 'job_posted_at_timestamp': 1770163200, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': '2026-02-04T00:00:00.000Z', 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3D0XpPcxNn12sGdgJGAAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': 'MONTH', 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113200', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': '_2YqPhD4vsBZpJqIAAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'General Software Engineer - Singapore', 'employer_name': 'WeRide', 'employer_logo': None, 'employer_website': 'https://www.weride.ai', 'job_publisher': 'Jooble', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://sg.jooble.org/jdp/2308038924519598264?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Jooble', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jooble.org/jdp/2308038924519598264?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Hiring Cafe', 'apply_link': 'https://hiring.cafe/viewjob/5wft764rovdtknuq?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Learn4Good', 'apply_link': 'https://www.learn4good.com/jobs/singapore/singapore/engineering/4851744752/e/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'BeBee SG', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.bebee.com/job/7d479ad73d1cf4dbc688137778a99631?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobrapido.com', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobrapido.com/jobpreview/5699329494070853632?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Recruit.net', 'apply_link': 'https://www.recruit.net/job/general-software-engineer-singapore-jobs/9116DDE6EBE8EB71?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://sg.jooble.org/jdp/2308038924519598264', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Jooble'}], 'job_description': 'Established in 2017, WeRide (NASDAQ: WRD) is a leading global commercial-stage company that develops autonomous driving technologies from Level 2 to Level 4. WeRide is the only tech company in the world that holds driverless permits in China, the UAE, Singapore and the US, conducting autonomous driving R&D, tests and operations in over 30 cities of 9 countries around the world. WeRide has operated a self-driving fleet for more than 1,800 days.\\n\\nWeRide (Singapore) is looking for world class coders to work on transforming mobility by solving some of the most challenging AI and robotics problems. You will work with world-class experts in the field of mobility solutions and advance the state of the art in areas such as computer vision, sensor fusion, machine learning, object tracking, and motion planning.\\n\\nRequirements:\\n• BS/MS/PhD degree in Robotics, Computer Science, Electrical Engineering or equivalent practical experience\\n• Experience in data structures and advanced algorithms\\n• Experience programming in C++\\n\\nPlus:\\n• Experience with field robotics and systems design\\n• Experience with robust, safety-critical, efficient code\\n• Experience in hands-on robotics research and expertise in one or more of the following: computer vision, LIDAR, object tracking, sensor fusion, perception, machine learning, motion planning, and control\\n\\nWeRide (Singapore) offers competitive salary and excellent employee benefits. Our office is located in the One-north area, a 5min walk from the one-north MRT station. If interested, please send your resume/CV to View email address on click.appcast.io.\\n\\nMore about WeRide:\\n\\nWebsite:\\n\\nYoutube:\\n\\nLinkedIn:\\n\\nTwitter:\\n\\nWe may use artificial intelligence (AI) tools to support parts of the hiring process, such as reviewing applications, analyzing resumes, or assessing responses. These tools assist our recruitment team but do not replace human judgment. Final hiring decisions are ultimately made by humans. If you would like more information about how your data is processed, please contact us.', 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': '7 days ago', 'job_posted_at_timestamp': 1771891200, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': '2026-02-24T00:00:00.000Z', 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3D_2YqPhD4vsBZpJqIAAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113200', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': 'CIbpWBxvCEAxbMF9AAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Lead Software Engineer, Java, Order Management System for Equities Trading', 'employer_name': 'JPMC Candidate Experience page', 'employer_logo': None, 'employer_website': None, 'job_publisher': 'JPMorgan Chase Login', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://jpmc.fa.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1001/job/210706194/?source=Zippia&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'JPMorgan Chase Login', 'apply_link': 'https://jpmc.fa.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1001/job/210706194/?source=Zippia&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Glassdoor', 'apply_link': 'https://www.glassdoor.sg/job-listing/lead-software-engineer-equities-trading-order-management-system-devops-jpmorgan-chase-co-JV_KO0,70_KE71,88.htm?jl=1010019665135&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'BeBee SG', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.bebee.com/job/5deabf7e38512904c398c89b208aa4b4?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'ALPFA Job Board', 'apply_link': 'https://jobs.alpfa.org/job/lead-software-engineer-java-order-management-system-for-equities-trading/82723968/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'NEXT Frontier Capital Job Board', 'apply_link': 'https://jobs.nextfrontiercapital.com/companies/aumni/jobs/66212642-lead-software-engineer-java-order-management-system-for-equities-trading?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Canary Wharfian', 'apply_link': 'https://www.canarywharfian.co.uk/jobs/jp-morgan/lead-software-engineer-java-equities-technology/b7862d78-1157-4951-a2a4-ad49971c8769?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Fairygodboss', 'apply_link': 'https://fairygodboss.com/jobs/jpmorganchase/lead-c-software-engineer-equities-trading-technologies-2d2a5ff5721b45ead84fd1231d48e035?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Hiring Cafe', 'apply_link': 'https://hiring.cafe/viewjob/s6ihg5xr52xojb7p?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://jpmc.fa.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1001/job/210706194/?source=Zippia', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'JPMorgan Chase Login'}], 'job_description': \"Be an integral part of an agile team that's constantly pushing the envelope to enhance, build, and deliver top-notch technology products.\\n\\nAs a Lead Software Engineer at JPMorgan Chase within the Corporate and Investment Banking, Equities - Structuring and Trading Technology team, you are an integral part of an agile team that works to enhance, build, and deliver trusted market-leading technology products in a secure, stable, and scalable way. Drive significant business impact through your capabilities and contributions, and apply deep technical expertise and problem-solving methodologies to tackle a diverse array of challenges that span multiple technologies and applications.\\n\\nJob responsibilities\\n• Regularly provides technical guidance and direction to support the business and its technical teams, contractors, and vendors\\n• Develops secure and high-quality production code, and reviews and debugs code written by others\\n• Drives decisions that influence the product design, application functionality, and technical operations and processes\\n• Serves as a function-wide subject matter expert in one or more areas of focus\\n• Actively contributes to the engineering community as an advocate of firmwide frameworks, tools, and practices of the Software Development Life Cycle\\n• Influences peers and project decision-makers to consider the use and application of leading-edge technologies\\n• Adds to the team culture of diversity, equity, inclusion, and respect\\n\\nRequired qualifications, capabilities, and skills\\n• Bachelor’s degree in computer science, Engineering, Mathematics, or other related disciplines\\n• 10 or more years of software engineering experience. Mastery in Java with respect to trading system designing, coding, testing , and software delivery\\n• Hands-on practical experience delivering system design, application development, testing, and operational stability\\n• Advanced in one or more programming language(s)\\n• Advanced knowledge of software applications and technical processes with considerable in-depth knowledge in one or more technical disciplines (e.g., cloud, artificial intelligence, machine learning, mobile, etc.)\\n• Ability to tackle design and functionality problems independently with little to no oversight\\n• Practical cloud native experience\\n• Experience in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Mathematics, or a related technical field\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DCIbpWBxvCEAxbMF9AAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '43415100', 'job_onet_job_zone': '2'}, {'job_id': 'SCzQiG3068-QCUK-AAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Senior Software Engineer, AI - Global Treasury Payment Network (Relocate to Singapore)', 'employer_name': 'Airwallex', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQfaO69mRzbhWgnbTcrDmU4cw6UsuO8972fQku6&s=0', 'employer_website': 'https://www.airwallex.com', 'job_publisher': 'Tech Jobs Personalized', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://builtin.com/job/senior-software-engineer-ai-global-treasury-payment-network-relocate-singapore/8190546?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Tech Jobs Personalized', 'apply_link': 'https://builtin.com/job/senior-software-engineer-ai-global-treasury-payment-network-relocate-singapore/8190546?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Glassdoor', 'apply_link': 'https://www.glassdoor.sg/job-listing/staff-software-engineer-backend-scale-relocate-to-singapore-airwallex-JV_KO0,59_KE60,69.htm?jl=1009964648497&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobstreet', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobstreet.com/job/87922849?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/staff-software-engineer-backend-scale-relocate-to-singapore-singapore-airwallex-5118-26515/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Founder-Led Hiring Platform, Axira AI Screening, Direct Matches & Scheduling', 'apply_link': 'https://foundersarehiring.com/job/on-site/senior-software-engineer-backend-stablecoin-relocate-to-singapore-68b7080213307205fa629f8b?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://builtin.com/job/senior-software-engineer-ai-global-treasury-payment-network-relocate-singapore/8190546', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Tech Jobs Personalized'}], 'job_description': 'About Airwallex\\nAirwallex is the only unified payments and financial platform for global businesses. Powered by our unique combination of proprietary infrastructure and software, we empower over 200,000 businesses worldwide - including Brex, Rippling, Navan, Qantas, SHEIN and many more - with fully integrated solutions to manage everything from business accounts, payments, spend management and treasury, to embedded finance at a global scale.\\nProudly founded in Melbourne, we have a team of over 2,000 of the brightest and most innovative people in tech across 26 offices around the globe. Valued at US$8 billion and backed by world-leading investors including T. Rowe Price, Visa, Mastercard, Robinhood Ventures, Sequoia, Salesforce Ventures, DST Global, and Lone Pine Capital, Airwallex is leading the charge in building the global payments and financial platform of the future. If you\\'re ready to do the most ambitious work of your career, join us.\\nAttributes We Value\\nWe hire successful builders with founder-like energy who want real impact, accelerated learning, and true ownership. You bring strong role-related expertise and sharp thinking, and you\\'re motivated by our mission and operating principles. You move fast with good judgment, dig deep with curiosity, and make decisions from first principles, balancing speed and rigor.\\nYou\\'re humble and collaborative; turn zero-to-one ideas into real products, and you \"get stuff done\" end-to-end. You use AI to work smarter and solve problems faster. Here, you\\'ll tackle complex, high-visibility problems with exceptional teammates and grow your career as we build the future of global banking. If that sounds like you, let\\'s build what\\'s next.\\nThe Opportunity:\\nThe Global Treasury and Payment Network (GTPN) team sits at the core of Airwallex\\'s payment infrastructure. As Airwallex\\'s very first product and still the largest revenue driver across the company, GTPN underpins many of our most critical customer experiences. We operate at the intersection of traditional and modern finance, expanding the reach of our global treasury and payment network, strengthening its capabilities and reliability, and delivering innovative payment products built on a robust financial foundation.\\nGTPN is a truly global, cross-site engineering organization, with talented engineers in existing and emerging hubs such as the US, Singapore, Hong Kong, and Shanghai. As we continue to scale worldwide, we\\'re looking for passionate Senior Software Engineers to join us. You\\'ll collaborate closely with product managers, designers, and engineers across regions to build and enhance products that not only meet but exceed our customers\\' expectations.\\nAbout the Role:\\nAs the senior engineer in our new Generative AI team, you will own the end-to-end development of AI-driven solutions that redefine how we provide support and automation for both internal teams and external customers. You will shape the underlying architecture and APIs for advanced systems building cutting-edge AI solutions that enable Airwallex to scale. Your contributions will directly influence innovation, set best practices, and establish the foundation for our expanding AI portfolio.\\nIf you are passionate about building AI solutions that directly impact customers, thrive on solving tough technical challenges, and embrace a product-focused mindset, we invite you to shape the future of Finance and AI with us.\\nResponsibilities:\\nBuild AI solutions to enable growth and drive internal efficiency across the business.\\nDesign and implement robust API and system architecture for new AI applications.\\nCollaborate closely with a cross-functional team to bring these AI solutions to life.\\nEmbrace the challenges of a fast-paced, high-growth environment with a focus on innovation.\\nMinimum qualifications:\\n• 5+ years in backend software development, with a focus on AI.\\n• Experience building internal or customer-facing products with LLMs.\\n• Expertise in building efficient, large-scale software systems.\\n• Skill in writing high-quality, maintainable code.\\n• Experience in design and development of large-scale distributed, high concurrency, high load, high availability systems;\\n• Excellent communication and mentoring abilities.\\n• A relevant degree in Computer Science, Mathematics or related fields.\\n\\nPreferred qualifications:\\n• Familiarity with MLOps practices and deployment pipelines for AI-driven products.\\n• Past experience in payments or FinTech.\\n\\nApplicant Safety Policy: Fraud and Third-Party Recruiters\\nTo protect you from recruitment scams, please be aware that Airwallex will not ask for bank details, sensitive ID numbers (i.e. passport), or any form of payment during the application or interview process. All official communication will come from an @airwallex.com email address. Please apply only through careers.airwallex.com or our official LinkedIn page.\\nAirwallex does not accept unsolicited resumes from search firms/recruiters. Airwallex will not pay any fees to search firms/recruiters if a candidate is submitted by a search firm/recruiter unless an agreement has been entered into with respect to specific open position(s). Search firms/recruiters submitting resumes to Airwallex on an unsolicited basis shall be deemed to accept this condition, regardless of any other provision to the contrary.\\nEqual opportunity\\nAirwallex is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. We value diversity and anyone seeking employment at Airwallex is considered based on merit, qualifications, competence and talent. We don\\'t regard color, religion, race, national origin, sexual orientation, ancestry, citizenship, sex, marital or family status, disability, gender, or any other legally protected status when making our hiring decisions. If you have a disability or special need that requires accommodation, please let us know.', 'job_is_remote': True, 'job_posted_at': '23 days ago', 'job_posted_at_timestamp': 1770508800, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': '2026-02-08T00:00:00.000Z', 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DSCzQiG3068-QCUK-AAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15111100', 'job_onet_job_zone': '5'}, {'job_id': 'IOH27yEUMDiqown8AAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Core Engineering, SDLC & Runtime, Software Engineer Lead, Vice President, Singapore', 'employer_name': 'Goldman Sachs', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQCIrWhHA6-Ewi2GaTiwmvSFxBnnHUBfn3oCPoE&s=0', 'employer_website': 'https://www.goldmansachs.com', 'job_publisher': 'Indeed', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://sg.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=80eabc15fb1546f3&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Indeed', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=80eabc15fb1546f3&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Glassdoor', 'apply_link': 'https://www.glassdoor.sg/job-listing/core-engineering-sdlc-runtime-software-engineer-lead-vice-president-singapore-goldman-sachs-JV_KO0,77_KE78,91.htm?jl=1009994503823&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/core-engineering-sdlc-runtime-software-engineer-lead-vice-president-singapore-singapore-goldman-sachs-72541b8b18e2/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobrapido.com', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobrapido.com/jobpreview/7467126136045043712?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Tech Job Finder', 'apply_link': 'https://www.techjobfinder.com/data-engineering/goldman-sachs-core-engineering-knowledge-graph-software-engineer-lead-vice-president-singapore/14157?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://sg.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=80eabc15fb1546f3', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Indeed'}], 'job_description': \"Monorepo SDLC Platform\\n\\nDeveloper Experience enables engineers to deliver services, products and platforms for their business. Increasingly the firm relies on technology to achieve its commercial goals and deliver value to shareholders thru innovative technology solutions. To achieve these ambitions, we must be able to empower our talented engineers by providing a developer environment that is attractive, matches their expectations, keeps them engaged and productive.\\n\\nResponsible for Goldman Sachs’ mission critical production platforms including:\\n• Private and public cloud computing platforms\\n• Distributed scheduling\\n• Security and critical infrastructure services\\n• API platform\\n• SDLC\\n• CI/CD\\n\\nOur aim is to innovate and drive technology solutions that will impact the bottom line for the firm. By joining us, you will be part of a diverse global technical team focusing on solving critical business problems.\\n\\nWork on a multi-year initiative to build out our strategic, highly scalable and resilient SDLC platform using cutting-edge technologies and streamlining processes for our engineers across the firm.\\n\\nHOW YOU WILL FULFILL YOUR POTENTIAL\\n• Drive the modernisation of SDLC platforms to be standardized, scalable, available and resilient\\n• Design, develop, test and document high-quality code in a structured, disciplined, and fast-moving environment\\n• Excel at building strong relationships with other engineers and enjoy collaboration\\n\\nSKILLS AND EXPERIENCE WE ARE LOOKING FOR\\n• General knowledge of multiple languages, and in-depth knowledge of at least one of: Python, Golang, Erlang, Java, C++;\\n• Expertise in commercial / open source build systems (Gradle / Bazel / Make) and strong knowledge of software change management systems\\n• Prior experience of Devops, SRE, infrastructure (storage / networks / etc.)\\n• Knowledgeable about running key business applications on Linux platforms and Linux internals\\n• Passionate about the software development process and facilitating high frequency / high quality change across a vibrant and diverse user community\\n• Team player, eager to work in a global organization\\n• Highly entrepreneurial and motivated\\n• Strong oral and written communication skills\\n\\nABOUT GOLDMAN SACHS\\n\\nAt Goldman Sachs, we commit our people, capital and ideas to help our clients, shareholders and the communities we serve to grow. Founded in 1869, we are a leading global investment banking, securities and investment management firm. Headquartered in New York, we maintain offices around the world.\\n\\nWe believe who you are makes you better at what you do. We're committed to fostering and advancing diversity and inclusion in our own workplace and beyond by ensuring every individual within our firm has a number of opportunities to grow professionally and personally, from our training and development opportunities and firmwide networks to benefits, wellness and personal finance offerings and mindfulness programs. about our culture, benefits, and people at GS.com/careers.\\n\\nWe’re committed to finding reasonable accommodations for candidates with special needs or disabilities during our recruiting process. : https://www.goldmansachs.com/careers/footer/disability-statement.html\\n\\n© The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc., 2025. All rights reserved.\\n\\nGoldman Sachs is an equal opportunity employer and does not discriminate on the basis of race, color, religion, sex, national origin, age, veterans status, disability, or any other characteristic protected by applicable law.\\n\\nWe Offer Best-In-Class Benefits\\n\\nHealthcare & Medical Insurance\\n\\nWe offer a wide range of health and welfare programs that vary depending on office location. These generally include medical, dental, short-term disability, long-term disability, life, accidental death, labor accident and business travel accident insurance.\\n\\nHoliday & Vacation Policies\\n\\nWe offer competitive vacation policies based on employee level and office location. We promote time off from work to recharge by providing generous vacation entitlements and a minimum of three weeks expected vacation usage each year.\\n\\nFinancial Wellness & Retirement\\n\\nWe assist employees in saving and planning for retirement, offer financial support for higher education, and provide a number of benefits to help employees prepare for the unexpected. We offer live financial education and content on a variety of topics to address the spectrum of employees’ priorities.\\n\\nHealth Services\\n\\nWe offer a medical advocacy service for employees and family members facing critical health situations, and counseling and referral services through the Employee Assistance Program (EAP). We provide Global Medical, Security and Travel Assistance and a Workplace Ergonomics Program. We also offer state-of-the-art on-site health centers in certain offices.\\n\\nFitness\\n\\nTo encourage employees to live a healthy and active lifestyle, some of our offices feature on-site fitness centers. For eligible employees we typically reimburse fees paid for a fitness club membership or activity (up to a pre-approved amount).\\n\\nChild Care & Family Care\\n\\nWe offer on-site child care centers that provide full-time and emergency back-up care, as well as mother and baby rooms and homework rooms. In every office, we provide advice and counseling services, expectant parent resources and transitional programs for parents returning from parental leave. Adoption, surrogacy, egg donation and egg retrieval stipends are also available.\\n\\nBenefits at Goldman Sachs\\n\\nRead more about the full suite of class-leading benefits our firm has to offer.\\n\\nOpportunity Overview CORPORATE TITLE Vice President OFFICE LOCATION(S) Singapore DIVISION Engineering Division\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DIOH27yEUMDiqown8AAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113200', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': 'zkHiTs9Dxqvfcjj0AAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Software Engineer- ML OSS- Singapore/Tokyo', 'employer_name': 'Databricks', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSThrxeHfeQZ7a59m7bT_8XD1BMWzLp3NlsYG3L&s=0', 'employer_website': 'https://www.databricks.com', 'job_publisher': 'ApplyBlast', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://applyblast.com/j/software-engineer-ml-oss-singaporetokyo/694239df6f09396825830125?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': True, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'ApplyBlast', 'apply_link': 'https://applyblast.com/j/software-engineer-ml-oss-singaporetokyo/694239df6f09396825830125?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': True}, {'apply_link': 'https://applyblast.com/j/software-engineer-ml-oss-singaporetokyo/694239df6f09396825830125', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'ApplyBlast'}], 'job_description': \"A Software Engineer on Databricks' AI OSS Ecosystem Team contributes to the development and maintenance of open-source AI/ML platforms that support model and agent lifecycles at scale. The role engages with the broader AI/ML community to advance AIOps and help ensure customers have access to cutting-edge tooling. It aligns with Databricks' mission to enable data teams to solve complex problems using data and AI.\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Tokyo, Japan', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': 'Tokyo', 'job_country': 'JP', 'job_latitude': 35.6764225, 'job_longitude': 139.650027, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DzkHiTs9Dxqvfcjj0AAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_min_salary': 119714, 'job_max_salary': 159340, 'job_salary_period': 'YEAR', 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15111100', 'job_onet_job_zone': '5'}, {'job_id': 'HMfYysh6OtJtKjxUAAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'General Software Engineer - Singapore', 'employer_name': 'WeRide.ai', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTp5StxO_qmC1dWTpcqdJiWPg4lTHfTNpH553cr&s=0', 'employer_website': 'https://www.weride.ai', 'job_publisher': 'Glassdoor', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://www.glassdoor.sg/job-listing/general-software-engineer-singapore-weride-JV_KO0,35_KE36,42.htm?jl=1009625283997&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': True, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Glassdoor', 'apply_link': 'https://www.glassdoor.sg/job-listing/general-software-engineer-singapore-weride-JV_KO0,35_KE36,42.htm?jl=1009625283997&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': True}, {'publisher': 'LinkedIn Singapore', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.linkedin.com/jobs/view/general-software-engineer-singapore-at-weride-4143822390?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/general-software-engineer-singapore-singapore-werideai-293-3323531/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'BeBee SG', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.bebee.com/job/52f9c0bb267a49a74f5ebf294b624b9b?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobrapido.com', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.jobrapido.com/jobpreview/584397811064242176?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jobilize', 'apply_link': 'https://www.jobilize.com/job/sg-queenstown-general-software-engineer-weride-hiring-now-job-immediately?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'ClickaJobs', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.clickajobs.com/jobs/software-engineering?id=31979054&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://www.glassdoor.sg/job-listing/general-software-engineer-singapore-weride-JV_KO0,35_KE36,42.htm?jl=1009625283997', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Glassdoor'}], 'job_description': 'Established in 2017, WeRide (NASDAQ: WRD) is a leading global commercial-stage company that develops autonomous driving technologies from Level 2 to Level 4. WeRide is the only tech company in the world that holds driverless permits in China, the UAE, Singapore and the US, conducting autonomous driving R&D, tests and operations in over 30 cities of 9 countries around the world. WeRide has operated a self-driving fleet for more than 1,800 days.\\n\\nWeRide (Singapore) is looking for world class coders to work on transforming mobility by solving some of the most challenging AI and robotics problems. You will work with world-class experts in the field of mobility solutions and advance the state of the art in areas such as computer vision, sensor fusion, machine learning, object tracking, and motion planning.\\n\\nRequirements:\\n• BS/MS/PhD degree in Robotics, Computer Science, Electrical Engineering or equivalent practical experience.\\n• Experience in data structures and advanced algorithms\\n• Experience programming in C++\\n\\nPlus:\\n• Experience with field robotics and systems design\\n• Experience with robust, safety-critical, efficient code.\\n• Experience in hands-on robotics research and expertise in one or more of the following: computer vision, LIDAR, object tracking, sensor fusion, perception, machine learning, motion planning, and control\\n\\nWeRide (Singapore) offers competitive salary and excellent employee benefits. Our office is located in the One-north area, a 5min walk from the one-north MRT station. If interested, please send your resume/CV to alex.mah@weride.ai.\\n\\nMore about WeRide:\\n\\nWebsite: https://www.weride.ai/\\n\\nYoutube: https://www.youtube.com/@WeRideAI\\n\\nLinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/werideai\\n\\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/weride_ai\\n\\nWe may use artificial intelligence (AI) tools to support parts of the hiring process, such as reviewing applications, analyzing resumes, or assessing responses. These tools assist our recruitment team but do not replace human judgment. Final hiring decisions are ultimately made by humans. If you would like more information about how your data is processed, please contact us.', 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': '27 days ago', 'job_posted_at_timestamp': 1770163200, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': '2026-02-04T00:00:00.000Z', 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DHMfYysh6OtJtKjxUAAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113200', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': 'dmF1oI2lYdQjKmPJAAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Senior Software Systems Engineer, Tech & PM', 'employer_name': 'HP', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS1MG4pgTIfmIBywyTasiWYZ6FISIUTBdeeBPgz&s=0', 'employer_website': None, 'job_publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/senior-software-systems-engineer-tech-pm-singapore-hp-293-3324854/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/senior-software-systems-engineer-tech-pm-singapore-hp-293-3324854/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/senior-software-systems-engineer-tech-pm-singapore-hp-293-3324854/', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini'}], 'job_description': \"A leading technology company in Singapore is seeking a Software Systems Engineer to oversee the design and implementation of robust software systems for commercial notebooks. The ideal candidate will have a master's degree in Computer Science and 7-10 years of experience in systems engineering. This role involves collaborating with cross-functional teams to ensure the delivery of high-quality software and firmware solutions. Competitive compensation is offered along with full-time employment.\\n#J-18808-Ljbffr\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': '1 day ago', 'job_posted_at_timestamp': 1772409600, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': '2026-03-02T00:00:00.000Z', 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://